17. How is the adoption of telematics and IoT impacting the truck hydraulic pump market?
The adoption of telematics and IoT in commercial vehicles is driving the demand for smart hydraulic systems, which monitor and optimize the performance of hydraulic pumps in trucks.

18. What are the technological advancements in truck hydraulic pump systems?
Technological advancements in truck hydraulic pump systems include the integration of sensors, electronic control units, and predictive maintenance capabilities for improved reliability and performance.

